Codility
















Hi AKSHATHA J BNMIT,
Thank you for your interest in Synamedia!

    As part of the hiring process, please complete the assessment linked below to showcase your technical skills by solving job-related problems.
    You will be asked to prepare code, answer technical questions, or both.
    Once submitted, your responses will be automatically scored and the results will be sent to Synamedia's hiring team. 


    For the best experience, please review the Codility Candidate FAQ before you begin.
    You can also try a practice problem to familiarize yourself with the testing environment.

When you're ready, please use the link below to begin the assessment. Further instructions will be provided.
Please complete the assessment by Jul 18, 2024, 05:00 UTC.
 https://app-eu.codility.com/test/NTMQCE-CYQ/ 
If you have any questions about the test or the hiring process, please reach out to your point of contact at Synamedia.
We know your time is valuable so thank you for spending some of it to show us what you can do! Thanks again for your interest in a role at Synamedia.

A company simulated online assessment will be conducted between 8th and 12th July 2024,post 6pm. as part of Mock placement drive.

Mock GD and Personal Interviews are scheduled on Saturday, 13th July 2024 (8:30am to 5pm).

Pre-Placement Connect by M/s Accenture.body:
Dear Students,

This is with reference to the Pre-Placement Connect by M/s Accenture on 23rd July 2024.

All of you are instructed to join the online session at 5:00 p.m. sharp without fail. PPC invite link and timings are given below.


[cid:c58a08fe-6c85-44e0-ad8c-1cdad30bd56e]

Meet us at our Pre-Placement Connect!
At the heart of every great change is a great human. Every day, our people do incredible things by working together to pursue our shared purpose–to deliver on the promise of technology and human ingenuity.

As you gear up to embark on your career journey, we would like to invite you to our Pre-Placement Connect. At Accenture, we offer boundaryless opportunities with limitless possibilities for charting a promising career. During this event, we will talk about how you can bring your skills, curiosity, and your best true self to work.

So, don’t miss this opportunity to meet our leaders and campus recruitment team, understand our recruitment process, and seek answers to your questions about starting a career at Accenture.
Date: 23rd July 2024
Time: 5:00 PM to 6:30 PM
Joining link: Join conversation (microsoft.com)<https://teams.microsoft.com/dl/launcher/launcher.html?url=%2F_%23%2Fl%2Fmeetup-join%2F19%3Ameeting_ZGY5NTBjYmYtMDI2MC00ZTA5LWEzNzgtMTk2ZDg4YTgwYmYw%40thread.v2%2F0%3Fcontext%3D%257B%2522Tid%2522%253A%2522e0793d39-0939-496d-b129-198edd916feb%2522%252C%2522Oid%2522%253A%252200644ff6-3e07-456c-8574-329f9b42055f%2522%252C%2522IsBroadcastMeeting%2522%253Atrue%252C%2522role%2522%253A%2522a%2522%257D%26btype%3Da%26role%3Da%26anon%3Dtrue&type=meetup-join&deeplinkId=62fb4fc6-eb0d-4256-9387-03e060a3f5a8&directDl=true&msLaunch=true&enableMobilePage=true&suppressPrompt=true>


Dr. Saritha Chakrasali
Head, Training & Placement
[cid:6c111ab7-7ad0-480b-ab61-cc26894288a5]
Vision: ​  ​To be one of the premier institutes of Engineering and Management education in the country.
​​Mission: To provide Engineering and Management education that meets the needs of human resources in the country.
​            ​    To develop leadership qualities, team spirit and concern for environment in students.

Dear Students,

This is a reminder to attend the Pre-Placement Connect by M/s Accenture on 23rd July 2024.

All of you are instructed to join the same on the link given below today at 5:00 p.m. sharp without fail.

Meet us at our Pre-Placement Connect!
At the heart of every great change is a great human. Every day, our people do incredible things by working together to pursue our shared purpose–to deliver on the promise of technology and human ingenuity.

As you gear up to embark on your career journey, we would like to invite you to our Pre-Placement Connect. Infosys Campus Recruitment Program: Appl.body:
[cid:image002.jpg@01DAB693.1A35C470]


Dear candidate,
Greetings from Infosys! Hope you and your loved ones are doing well.
We have received your nomination for the Infosys Campus Recruitment Program 2024-25 from your institute. Graduates from the 2025 batch will be hired for the role of Specialist Programmer through this program.
Please fill out the application form<https://surveys.infosysapps.com/r/a/Infosys_SPregistration2025campusbatch> before Friday, July 26, 2024 to apply for the program. We will shortlist the candidates for this recruitment process based on the details received through the application form. Please note, this is a mandatory step as part of the process. Candidates who do not fill the application form will not be considered.
Link for application - Click Here<https://surveys.infosysapps.com/r/a/Infosys_SPregistration2025campusbatch>
Infosys Campus Recruitment Program will be conducted in a phased manner comprising of Infosys online test and in-person interview. Candidates who clear the Infosys online test will proceed to the interview round. Attached guidelines and sample test paper are for your reference and preparation.

In case of any queries, please write to talent.acquisition@infosys.com<mailto:talent.acquisition@infosys.com>. Recruitment related emails sent to any other email address will not be responded to. We look forward to interacting with you.

Talent Acquisition Team,
Infosys

In the coming weeks, Google Play will launch new personalization options  
that give you more seamless control of your personalization preferences and  
allow you to better manage your data in Play.

Personalization provides a richer experience in the Play store, helping you  
discover exciting games, useful apps, relevant offers and much more, all of

Lowe's companies, Inc. (NYSE: LOW) is a FORTUNE® 50 home improvement company serving approximately 16 million customer transactions a week in the United States. With total fiscal year 2023 sales of more than $86 billion, Lowe's operates over 1,700 home improvement stores and employs approximately 300,000 associates. Based in Bengaluru, Lowe's India develops innovative technology products and solutions and delivers business capabilities to provide the best omnichannel experience for Lowe's customers. Lowe's India employs over 4,200 associates across technology, analytics, merchandising, supply chain, marketing, finance and accounting, product management and shared services. Lowe's India actively supports the communities it serves through programs focused on skill-building, sustainability, and safe homes.

Infosys Springboard Internship 5.0 Nomin.body:
[cid:image004.png@01DAE1C4.585DE8C0]

Dear Learner,
We are thrilled to announce the launch of the 5th edition for Infosys Springboard Internship. Our internship program has been a launchpad for aspiring enthusiasts, providing a platform to work on real-world projects and gain exposure to the latest technologies. The previous batches have seen interns excel and move forward with a wealth of knowledge and practical experience.
What's in it for you?



  1.  In-depth Technical Knowledge: Gain hands-on experience in your chosen field of technology.
  2.  Project-Based Learning: Gain practical experience of working on a project.
  3.  Expert Guidance: Learn from industry leaders and become part of a community of like-minded individuals.

Who can apply?




  *   Undergraduate and Postgraduate Students: Specifically, those in their 3rd or 4th year of college/university.

How to Apply?



  1.  Pick a technology area* (AI, Angular Full Stack, Python, Java Tech Stack or Data Visualization) you would be most interested in for the projects.
  2.  Fill the following nomination form:

Click here to Nominate<https://infyspringboard.onwingspan.com/web/en/page/embed-gno?survey=2138>


*Click here<https://infyspringboard.onwingspan.com/web/en/page/lex_auth_01398268320967884838> to start your learning journey under your chosen technology area.
For e.g., if you opted for Artificial Intelligence, start with the courses listed under "Artificial Intelligence - Learning Path."

The deadline to complete the nomination for Internship is August 6, 2024 & the deadline to complete recommended courses of your chosen technology theme is August 20, 2024.

Important Notes:



  *   Slots are filled on a first-come, first-serve basis. Nomination link will be active only till slots are available on this basis.
  *   This internship aims to give project experience to students, hence working professionals and alumni of previous batch need not apply for this program.
  *   Registration does not confirm internship. Only those registrants completing the recommended courses on Infosys Springboard and criteria within deadline will be offered internship.

In case of queries, write to springboard-support@infosys.com<mailto:springboard-support@infosys.com>.

We look forward to seeing you among this batch of interns!

Regards,
Team Infosys Springboard

Sananda Rao K S shared a post: STOP believing these if you want to grow in your career


I’ve coached 40+ professionals 1-on-1. 

During our sessions, I don’t just teach them 
I get to understand their mindset.

After spending 900+ hours with professionals at different stages of their careers, I’ve realized:

📌 What you *believe* can make or break your career

Here are 13 limiting beliefs that are blocking your career growth:

“I can’t get a better-paying job in this market condition”
“I don’t have enough experience to get a salary hike”
“I’m not confident enough to talk to other people”
“My income will increase only if I go abroad”
“I can’t earn lakhs of rupees per month”
“I can’t grow because of office politics”
“I’m not ready for the promotion yet”
“I can’t do many things in a day”
“I’m not good at selling”
“I’m not worth it”
“I’m a failure”
“I’m bored”
“I’m lazy”

You become what you believe.

If you don't have any of these limiting beliefs - Congratulations! 
You are on the right track and you're most probably killing it in your career!

But if you believe even a few of these - 
Change what you believe about yourself.

Trust me, your life will start changing.

PS: What limiting beliefs do you have?

Share it in the comments and I’ll help you frame a new positive belief.

#limitingbeliefs #mindset #careergrowth
